    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214650/extras/8ef5bf185e3567630396ab4f0f9e96e1.poster.avif?t=1723428775\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214650/extras/8ef5bf185e3567630396ab4f0f9e96e1.webm?t=1723428775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214650/extras/8ef5bf185e3567630396ab4f0f9e96e1.mp4?t=1723428775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>R在这款令人愉快的益智平台游戏中，带领一群可爱的Rolando不断翻滚，展开冒险！与爬墙的尖刺突击队、沉睡的爱德华国王、倒霉的格拉德斯通王子和神秘的菲戈蒙托联手，利用他们的独特能力和技能组合，穿越千变万化的环境，克服重重挑战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214650/extras/38dff2acf82022342605b7125ee83ff2.poster.avif?t=1723428775\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214650/extras/38dff2acf82022342605b7125ee83ff2.webm?t=1723428775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214650/extras/38dff2acf82022342605b7125ee83ff2.mp4?t=1723428775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Rolando王国充满了强大的“灵物”，你可以直接控制这些特殊装置来协助冒险。释放炸弹大炮，利用光束，建造魔法桥，操纵风扇，掌控电梯，辅助你的Rolando执行崇高的任务。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214650/extras/f9e3e1af6550d2991bbd0276abd9ff46.poster.avif?t=1723428775\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214650/extras/f9e3e1af6550d2991bbd0276abd9ff46.webm?t=1723428775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214650/extras/f9e3e1af6550d2991bbd0276abd9ff46.mp4?t=1723428775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你将会体验到各种各样的游戏方式：从动感十足的平台游戏（如跳跃危险裂口，在岩层中炸出道路）到各种趣味游戏，如引人入胜的解谜、秘密狩猎和护送打盹的皇室成员。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214650/extras/04ee549e4fe1ab5de63b822a8a673767.poster.avif?t=1723428775\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214650/extras/04ee549e4fe1ab5de63b822a8a673767.webm?t=1723428775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214650/extras/04ee549e4fe1ab5de63b822a8a673767.mp4?t=1723428775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>沉浸在芬兰艺术家Mikko Walamies打造的栩栩如生、活力四射的迷人世界中。遇到讨喜又好奇的角色时，你会情不自禁地露出微笑。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214650/extras/43f0668fc5a9d700148a5c980e37861e.poster.avif?t=1723428775\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214650/extras/43f0668fc5a9d700148a5c980e37861e.webm?t=1723428775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214650/extras/43f0668fc5a9d700148a5c980e37861e.mp4?t=1723428775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>穿越迷人的Rolando王国的每个角落，英勇地探索，从暗影生物的魔掌中拯救出睿智的圣人。从阳光普照的霍尼卡布草甸山丘到不祥的暗影山谷深处，每个世界都会带来独特的体验和一系列新的挑战。开始翻滚吧！",
